[[File:Annaes Maritimos e Coloniaes (Page 1) BHL6689018.jpg|thumb|right|180px|''Annaes Maritimos e Coloniaes'', 1846]]
The '''Associação Maritima e Colonial''' (Maritime and Colonial Association) of [[Portugal]] formed in 1839.{{sfn|Silvestre Ribeiro|1879}} Officials included Joaquim Jose Goncalves de Mattos Correia, Joaquim Jose Cecilia Kol, and {{illm|José Xavier Bressane Leite|pt}}.{{sfn|Silvestre Ribeiro|1879}} In the 1840s it issued a monthly journal, ''[[Annaes Maritimos e Coloniaes]].''<ref name=Rafael2001>{{cite book|editor1=Gina Guedes Rafael |editor2= Manuela Santos |title=Jornais e revistas portugueses do século XIX|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=Qu6pnMf5jfEC|year=2001 |publisher=[[Biblioteca Nacional de Portugal|Biblioteca Nacional]] |isbn=978-972-565-229-9 |language=pt }}</ref>

