'''Far Reaching Ministries''' is a non-profit mission organization founded by Wes Bentley that assists the people of [[Africa]], with a focus on [[Sudan]], [[Uganda]] and [[Kenya]]. They have been helping the [[Night Commuters]] of Northern Uganda in [[Kitgum]] and [[Gulu]].<ref>http://www.farreachingministries.org/</ref><ref>http://www.truthcasting.com/Calvary-Chapel-OxnardCA-God-Does-Cool-Stuff-22964.sermon</ref>

