[[Image:Gudbrandsbiblia.jpg|right|thumb|150px|Guðbrandur published the first complete [[Icelandic language|Icelandic]] translation of the [[bible]] in 1584.]]

'''Guðbrand's Bible''' ({{lang-is|'''Guðbrandsbiblía'''}}) was the first [[Icelandic language]] translation of the [[Bible]]. The translation was completed in 1584 by [[Guðbrandur Þorláksson]], bishop of [[Hólar]].

