[[File:Air Vice Marshal Michael Samson-Oje.jpg|thumb|Samson-Oje at the USAF Regional African Air Chiefs Symposium in Accra.]]

[[Air Marshal]] '''Michael Samson-Oje''' (born 5 January 1954) is a senior commander in the [[Ghana Air Force]] and the current Ghanaian [[Chief of the Defence Staff (Ghana)|Chief of Defence Staff]]. Prior to that he was Chief of Air Staff.  Before his appointment as Air Force chief, Samson-Oje was Station Commander of Takoradi Air Base.

