{{Expand Italian|Diocesi di Uije|date=February 2011}} The '''Roman Catholic Diocese of Uíje''' ({{lang-la|Dioecesis Uiiensis}}) is a [[diocese]] located in [[Uíje]] in the [[Ecclesiastical province]] of [[Roman Catholic Archdiocese of Malanje|Malanje]] in [[Angola]].
==History== * March 14, 1967: Established as Diocese of Carmona and São Salvador from the [[Metropolitan Archdiocese of Luanda]] * May 16, 1979: Renamed as Diocese of Uíje
==Special churches== The Cathedral of the diocese is Sé Catedral de Nossa Senhora da Conceição (Cathedral Church of the Conception of Our Lady) in Uije .
==Leadership== * [[Bishop]]s of Uíje (Roman rite) ** Bishop [[Emilio Sumbelelo]] (since 2008.02.02) ** Bishop [[José Francisco Moreira dos Santos]], [[O.F.M. Cap.]] (1979.05.16 – 2008.02.02), retired * Bishops of Carmona and São Salvador (Roman rite) ** Bishop José Francisco Moreira dos Santos, O.F.M. Cap. (1967.03.14 – 1979.05.16)
==See also== *[[Roman Catholicism in Angola]]
==References== * [http://www.gcatholic.org/dioceses/diocese/uije0.htm GCatholic.org]
